pull_request.body:
This adds generation of a location-independent .tar.gz file containing all HTML, JS, CSS components containing the most recent test run results.
Options for distribution: a) Opening up the S3 folder for download where it is stored; b) adding an `scp` command to ship it somewhere.
Will work fully correctly only after PR #9 is merged and conflicts get resolved.
